column5: RATE EVERGREEN LODGE PLEASE ON EAGLE LAKE IN CANADA...
Don't know about Evergreen on Eagle lake but can tell you that EVERGREEN ON LAC SEUL is a great place to stay. Mike Kansas

We were there this past July for the first time, and liked it a lot. Excellent food, very helpful staff, clean cabins, and most importantly, great job filleting the y-bones out of our northern. Mal runs a very nice business. Dave
